{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/bridgetownrb/building-with-bridgetown/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Konnor's Blog","author":"Konnor Rogers"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8ce923f3-313d-5ef3-ae16-35fc7badb36a","excerpt":"This will be the actual building portion of creating a site with\nBridgetown To go back and see how the project is setup, check out Dockerizing\nBridgetown…","html":"<h2 id=\"foreword\">\n  <a href=\"#foreword\">\n    Prerequisites\n  </a>\n</h2>\n<p>This will be the actual building portion of creating a site with\n<a href=\"https://bridgetownrb.com\">Bridgetown</a></p>\n<p>To go back and see how the project is setup, check out <a href=\"bridgetownrb/dockerizing-bridgetown/\">Dockerizing\nBridgetown</a></p>\n<p>Alternatively, to follow along you could simply do the following:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"5515167515303121000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`git clone https://github.com/ParamagicDev/getting-started-with-bridgetown\n\ncd getting-started-with-bridgetown\nrm -rf .git\ngit init\nsource ./docker.env && docker-compose up --build`, `5515167515303121000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/ParamagicDev/getting-started-with-bridgetown\n\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> getting-started-with-bridgetown\n<span class=\"token function\">rm</span> -rf .git\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> init\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> ./docker.env <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> docker-compose up --build</code></pre></div>\n<p>And now you’re completely caught up! Lets get building!</p>\n<h2 id=\"site-data\">\n  <a href=\"#site-data\">\n    Setting Site Data\n  </a>\n</h2>\n<p>The first thing we want to do is setup some static data for us to pull\nin.</p>\n<p>For example, we want our <code class=\"language-text\">first_name</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">last_name</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">github_profile</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">linkedin_profile</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">portfolio_site</code> and whatever else\nyou can think of to be easily pulled down and easily changed should\nsomething change in the future.</p>\n<p>So where do we go to set site data?</p>\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://www.bridgetownrb.com/docs/datafiles\">Bridgetown\nDocs</a> you set up your\nstatic data inside of the <code class=\"language-text\">./_data/</code> directory. You can use one <code class=\"language-text\">YAML</code>,\n<code class=\"language-text\">JSON</code>, or <code class=\"language-text\">CSV</code> files. I prefer <code class=\"language-text\">YAML</code> myself.</p>\n<p>So lets add the data. Navigate to the <code class=\"language-text\">_data/site_metadata.yml</code> file.\nFor me, I filled in the following information:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"33741546639240140000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`# _data/site_metadata.yml\n\ntitle: Konnor's Portfolio\nemail: konnor7414@gmail.com\ndescription: >- # this means to ignore newlines\n  This is Konnor's portfolio site. It contains info about who he is, what\n  projects he is working on / has worked on, as well as contact information.\n\nfirst_name: Konnor\nlast_name: Rogers`, `33741546639240140000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token comment\"># _data/site_metadata.yml</span>\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Konnor's Portfolio\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">email</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> konnor7414@gmail.com\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">description</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># this means to ignore newlines</span>\n  This is Konnor's portfolio site. It contains info about who he is<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> what\n  projects he is working on / has worked on<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> as well as contact information.\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">first_name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Konnor\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">last_name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Rogers</code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"@todo\">Reference File on Github</a></p>\n<p>Now, lets create a <code class=\"language-text\">_data/projects.yml</code> file. Here, we can do things\nlike add links, descriptions, etc for each project that we plan on\nputting in. Heres what my <code class=\"language-text\">_data/projects.yml</code> file looks like.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"47137239044130770000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`# _data/projects.yml\n\nma_protocol_rewrite:\n  source_code: https://github.com/ParamagicDev/ma-protocol-rewrite/tree/master\n  deployed_app: https://inspiring-varahamihira-efb922.netlify.app/\n  description: ->\n    A rewrite of EMS protocols for the state of Massachusetts. The app\n    is written in React / Gatsby and attempts to created a more\n    navigable and searchable interface for reading the protocols. This is the\n    current project im working on.\n# Below projects omitted for brevity`, `47137239044130770000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token comment\"># _data/projects.yml</span>\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">ma_protocol_rewrite</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">source_code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>//github.com/ParamagicDev/ma<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>protocol<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>rewrite/tree/master\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">deployed_app</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>//inspiring<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>varahamihira<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>efb922.netlify.app/\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">description</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span><span class=\"token scalar string\">\n    A rewrite of EMS protocols for the state of Massachusetts. The app\n    is written in React / Gatsby and attempts to created a more\n    navigable and searchable interface for reading the protocols. This is the\n    current project im working on.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Below projects omitted for brevity</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"@todo\">Reference File on Github</a></p>\n<p>Finally, lets add some links for people to find us:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"49086661632645276000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`# _data/links.yml\n\nblog: https://paramagicdev.github.io/my-blog\nlinkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/in/konnor-rogers-78b120175/\ngithub: https://github.com/ParamagicDev`, `49086661632645276000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token comment\"># _data/links.yml</span>\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">blog</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>//paramagicdev.github.io/my<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>blog\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">linkedin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>//www.linkedin.com/in/konnor<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>rogers<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>78b120175/\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">github</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>//github.com/ParamagicDev</code></pre></div>\n<p>So now, in various pages we can access our data via a simple:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container customButtonContainerClass\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"81274166146910300000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied to clipboard!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`# Example Page\n\n{{ site.links.github }}\nhttps://github.com/ParamagicDev\n\n{{ site.projects.ma_protocol_rewrite[:source_code] }}\nhttps://github.com/ParamagicDev/ma-protocol-rewrite/tree/master\n\n{{ site.site_metadata.first_name }}\nKonnor`, `81274166146910300000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"Copy to clipboard\"\n              >\n                <svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"md\"><pre class=\"language-md\"><code class=\"language-md\"><span class=\"token title important\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">#</span> Example Page</span>\n\n{{ site.links.github }}\nhttps://github.com/ParamagicDev\n\n{{ site.projects.ma<span class=\"token italic\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">_</span><span class=\"token content\">protocol</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">_</span></span>rewrite[:source_code] }}\nhttps://github.com/ParamagicDev/ma-protocol-rewrite/tree/master\n\n{{ site.site<span class=\"token italic\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">_</span><span class=\"token content\">metadata.first</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">_</span></span>name }}\nKonnor</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Building with Bridgetown - Portfolio","date":"May 24, 2020","description":"In this post, I will be detailing how I built my portfolio site with Bridgetown along with TailwindCSS."}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/bridgetownrb/building-with-bridgetown/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/bridgetownrb/dockerizing-bridgetown/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Dockerizing Bridgetown"}},"next":null}}}